description: Crawfish is southern seafood at its very best, and you'll never find better crawfish in all of Alabama then what they're serving up at Red Mountain Crawfish Company! Superb shellfish coming straight from Louisiana always makes for a delicious dish, and this truck is dishing it out every time you try them. Crawfish, crab, shrimp, and so much more are right around the corner, so don't miss out on the fantastic food from Red Mountain Crawfish Company!
name: Red Mountain Crawfish Company
